{"tid":2513424,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家覺唔覺電腦打中文字，既關聯詞，好落後？","createTime":"2021-05-02T13:22:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T13:40:32.000Z","uid":118571,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ea2b2e931dd8db927072f4d47980006f26c59f19","tid":2513424,"uid":118571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T13:22:27.000Z","msg":"大家覺唔覺電腦打中文字，既關聯詞，好落後？<br />\n<br />\n例如：打個&ldquo;迪&rdquo;字，關聯唔到&ldquo;迪士尼&rdquo;呢個詞語，咁就要三個字分開打<br />\n<br />\n變相，我起手機打字仲快過起電腦打字<br />\n<br />\n仲有，一些常用字，例如：過，覺，箱，高，矮，等，特，得，<br />\n打速成既話，佢地唔起第一頁，要禁space去一頁或下兩三四頁先搵到隻字，<br />\n&ldquo;過&rdquo;字就係例子，要space到第四頁先打到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：本人唔係唔識打字，但只識打速成，而係起電腦比較少打中文字，有時一啲比較少打不常打既字，可能真係要用啲時間先搵到"},{"pid":"b132ab1128a3adfbaabcffc48b944bae54ae5a4d","tid":2513424,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T13:23:51.000Z","msg":"電腦啲輸入法不嬲廢"},{"pid":"5de9bccdff89d3223f52117f048e5fe29fd1e8b9","tid":2513424,"uid":118571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T13:23:54.000Z","msg":"當然，會有人打慣打熟可能真係冇問題，記得晒啲排位，閉眼都打到"},{"pid":"d05f16845ce0d740945e745e68b8d7d33b31610e","tid":2513424,"uid":118571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b132ab1128a3adfbaabcffc48b944bae54ae5a4d","tid":2513424,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T13:23:51.000Z","msg":"電腦啲輸入法不嬲廢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T13:24:58.000Z","msg":"我覺得係廿幾年不變"},{"pid":"e76dfb56e2f218a5c4bff60cfef2522c16b209ad","tid":2513424,"uid":98403,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T13:25:18.000Z","msg":"iPhone 速成會按常用度排 windows 應該學吓"},{"pid":"0eaf8dddb6a412b6b78d334fbb8918f71bd0871f","tid":2513424,"uid":138868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T13:26:32.000Z","msg":"我都覺<br />\n可能因為電腦唔會update關聯字表？<br />\n手機嘅話如果有樣嘢最近多人講<br />\n有機會前咗（感覺上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4703714fa37d41e1f7e